<abstract><t>The objective of the PPSP work is to standardize the key signaling protocols that apply to tracker and peers in a Peer-to-Peer (P2P) streaming system.  These protocols are called PPSP.  This document enumerates the requirements for the PPSP, which should be considered when designing PPSP.</t></abstract>

